    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18.598" end="00:00:22.177">Um, dois. Um, dois, tr&#234;s, quatro.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.255" end="00:00:23.496"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23.558" end="00:00:25.665">Se gosta da m&#250;sica de James Brown,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.665" end="00:00:27.557">esta noite vai passar um bom bocado.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.557" end="00:00:29.731">Esta noite estamos a celebrar o 62&#186; anivers&#225;rio</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.731" end="00:00:33.816">de Black Velvet, James Brown Jr.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33.816" end="00:00:35.870" region="top">Whoo, 62! </p>
      <p begin="00:00:36.439" end="00:00:38.487" region="top">Agora, comecem a bater palmas </p>
      <p begin="00:00:38.487" end="00:00:39.718" region="top">porque temos um jovem </p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.718" end="00:00:41.503" region="top">prestes a subir ao palco. </p>
      <p begin="00:00:41.503" end="00:00:43.646">Ele esteve no programa do David Letterman</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.646" end="00:00:45.731">Batam palmas, conhe&#231;am e cumprimentem</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.731" end="00:00:49.913">ao Black Velvet, James Brown, Jr.!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.913" end="00:00:52.226"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52.226" end="00:00:53.898"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53.898" end="00:00:59.189">&#9834; &#201; um mundo de homem. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.189" end="00:01:05.490">&#9834; Mas eu n&#227;o seria nada, nada... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05.490" end="00:01:06.648">- Imito o James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.648" end="00:01:13.882">desde os meus 14 anos.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.882" end="00:01:16.398"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16.398" end="00:01:17.857"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17.857" end="00:01:21.189"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21.189" end="00:01:25.774"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25.774" end="00:01:29.677">Mas agora vou come&#231;ar a fazer de Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.677" end="00:01:52.332"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52.486" end="00:01:54.356" region="top">O meu primeiro &#225;lbum de originais </p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.356" end="00:01:58.013" region="top">vai ficar &#224; venda em 25 de Janeiro. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.013" end="00:02:01.149">H&#225; 42 anos que luto</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.149" end="00:02:02.890">para singrar na ind&#250;stria</p>
      <p begin="00:02:02.890" end="00:02:04.606">e, aos 62 anos,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.606" end="00:02:06.648">estou a come&#231;ar a encontrar o meu caminho.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.956" end="00:02:10.939">Nunca fiz dinheiro suficiente</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.939" end="00:02:13.794">para me sustentar no mundo da m&#250;sica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.794" end="00:02:15.857">,as espero que este &#225;lbum</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.857" end="00:02:17.304">seja um ponto de viragem para mim,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.304" end="00:02:20.111">e que me possa sustentar atrav&#233;s da m&#250;sica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.168" end="00:02:26.690">Hey, man.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.690" end="00:02:28.659">Vou buscar-te &#225;gua, ok?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.659" end="00:02:30.004">Hey, man.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.004" end="00:02:30.683">Este &#233; o meu p&#225;ssaro.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.683" end="00:02:32.494">Deixa-me louco.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32.494" end="00:02:33.628">Fico zangado, saio da beira dele, vou para as traseiras, fecho a porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.628" end="00:02:35.364">Eu vou no quarto, fechar a porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.364" end="00:02:37.170">e deixo-o &#224; vontade para gritar quanto ele quiser.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:37.861" end="00:02:38.897">E ter a minha casinha est&#225;vel,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.897" end="00:02:40.429">n&#227;o &#233; tudo o que quero,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.429" end="00:02:43.035">mas gra&#231;as a Deus que tenho um telhado sobre a cabe&#231;a.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.056" end="00:02:45.363">Quando entro no meu apartamentozinho</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.363" end="00:02:46.945">e fecho a minha porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:46.945" end="00:02:48.565">fico em paz.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48.565" end="00:02:50.325">Mas quando entro nos bairros,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.325" end="00:02:53.051">quando entro no elevador,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.051" end="00:02:54.132">entrar l&#225;,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54.132" end="00:02:55.369">&#233; a&#237; que come&#231;am os sarilhos.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.369" end="00:02:56.898">Nunca se sabe</p>
      <p begin="00:02:56.898" end="00:02:58.994">o que vai acontecer nessas noites.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:58.994" end="00:03:00.482">O tipo l&#225; de baixo,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.482" end="00:03:02.183">o nome dele &#233; Alfred,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.183" end="00:03:03.022">Tipo muito bom, n&#227;o chateia ningu&#233;m.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.022" end="00:03:04.598">&#201; um tipo religioso.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.598" end="00:03:06.544">Eles dispararam contra a casa dele.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.544" end="00:03:07.565">Ele mostrou-me todos os buracos</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07.565" end="00:03:08.289">onde foram disparados tiros.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.289" end="00:03:09.071">Eu disse: "Wow, man."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.071" end="00:03:10.550">Eu disse,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.550" end="00:03:12.823">N&#227;o era capaz de viver no r&#233;s-do-ch&#227;o.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.823" end="00:03:14.391">Quando as coisas ficam</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.391" end="00:03:16.092">demasiado m&#225;s nos bairros,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.092" end="00:03:17.808">vou para casa da minha m&#227;e</p>
      <p begin="00:03:17.808" end="00:03:19.537">e durmo na cave dela.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.862" end="00:03:33.477">Ent&#227;o venho para aqui,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33.477" end="00:03:35.794">e &#233; aqui que durmo.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:35.794" end="00:03:37.051">At&#233; ao dia seguinte,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37.051" end="00:03:38.838">vou fazer os recados,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:38.838" end="00:03:39.884">cuidar de tudo o que precisamos</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.884" end="00:03:43.414">para manter o telhado sobre ambas as nossas cabe&#231;as.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.707" end="00:03:47.142">Gosto de enrolar um pouco disto</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.142" end="00:03:48.735">na forma de uma pequena bola.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50.722" end="00:03:53.068">&#201; s&#243; meter estes l&#225; dentro.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.486" end="00:03:56.661">Hey, como est&#225; o arroz?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:56.829" end="00:03:58.127">- Deixa-me ver</p>
      <p begin="00:03:59.894" end="00:04:01.813">S&#243; mais um bocadinho.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:01.951" end="00:04:04.880">- Venho de uma fam&#237;lia de oito pessoas.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:04.942" end="00:04:07.772">O meu objectivo principal &#233; tomar conta</p>
      <p begin="00:04:07.772" end="00:04:11.547">da minha m&#227;e, e fazer o melhor que posso.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.454" end="00:04:14.409" region="top">- &#201; o meu menino, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.409" end="00:04:16.520" region="top">e adoro-o. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.626" end="00:04:18.297" region="top">Ele lava a minha roupa. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.467" end="00:04:19.206" region="top">Ele limpa a casa. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.206" end="00:04:20.684" region="top">No Dia dos Namorados, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.684" end="00:04:23.291" region="top">comprou-me uma caixa de chocolates. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:23.291" end="00:04:24.646" region="top">E o meu menino &#233; t&#227;o docinho </p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.646" end="00:04:25.871" region="top">quanto esses chocolates. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:25.871" end="00:04:27.567">Apenas fa&#231;o com que ela</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.567" end="00:04:28.273">tenha uma vida calma,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.273" end="00:04:29.398">e</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29.398" end="00:04:31.440">ent&#227;o, ela n&#227;o tmr que se preocupar</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.440" end="00:04:33.038">com contas nem nada.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.038" end="00:04:34.203">Assumi esse fardo,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.203" end="00:04:35.913">e n&#227;o sabia mesmo</p>
      <p begin="00:04:35.913" end="00:04:36.953">em que me estava a meter.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:36.953" end="00:04:38.214">Mas agora, j&#225; me comprometi.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.214" end="00:04:39.802">N&#227;o vou mudar.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:39.802" end="00:04:40.970">Ent&#227;o a &#250;nica coisa que posso &#233; tentar</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.970" end="00:04:42.685">fazer com que algo funcione</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.685" end="00:04:44.012">onde possa arranjar um rendimento decente</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.012" end="00:04:46.923">para que eu possa viver e deixar viver.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.923" end="00:04:49.739">E isso &#233; tudo o que posso pedir da vida agora.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:49.847" end="00:04:56.578"/>
      <p begin="00:04:56.578" end="00:05:00.314">&#9834; And&#225;mos &#224;s voltas outra vez.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.314" end="00:05:04.916">&#9834; Onde p&#225;ra, ningu&#233;m sabe. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:04.916" end="00:05:08.256">&#9834; &#201; um frio, frio mundo. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.656" end="00:05:12.156">&#9834; &#201; um frio, frio mundo. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.939" end="00:05:15.856">&#9834; Como podemos parar as mudan&#231;as &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:15.856" end="00:05:20.897">&#9834; que decorrem na Am&#233;rica hoje? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.701" end="00:05:34.686">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.124" end="00:05:43.231">&#9834; Regressar. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.231" end="00:05:46.939">&#9834; Regressar &#224; Regra Dourada. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:46.939" end="00:05:48.645">&#9834; Oh. Ah. Uh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.105" end="00:05:50.612">&#9834; Regressar &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.612" end="00:05:55.148">&#9834; Regressar &#224; Regra Dourada. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.148" end="00:05:57.856">&#9834; Bring it all down. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.856" end="00:06:11.472"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11.472" end="00:06:13.064">- Esta &#233; uma m&#250;sica</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13.064" end="00:06:15.023">do novo &#225;lbum, No Time for Dreaming.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15.023" end="00:06:16.148">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.148" end="00:06:17.274">e a Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.274" end="00:06:18.731">N&#227;o consigo acreditar</p>
      <p begin="00:06:18.731" end="00:06:20.064">que tenhas aparecido do nada,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.064" end="00:06:22.273">virtualmente desconhecido para n&#243;s.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.273" end="00:06:24.473">J&#225; gravou alguma vez antes?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.596" end="00:06:25.890">- N&#227;o.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:25.890" end="00:06:28.431">&#201; a primeira vez em que realmente come&#231;o a aparecer.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28.431" end="00:06:29.958">- Sei que tem actuado.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:29.958" end="00:06:31.039">- Sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31.039" end="00:06:32.027">- Como Black Velvet</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32.027" end="00:06:33.649">- Sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:33.649" end="00:06:34.939">- Ent&#227;o agora est&#225; a actuar como-</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.939" end="00:06:36.666">como Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:36.666" end="00:06:37.677">- Sim, sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.677" end="00:06:38.898">- Bem, tem uma &#243;ptima banda</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38.898" end="00:06:39.728">a apoi&#225;-lo.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.728" end="00:06:41.265">E, claro,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.265" end="00:06:42.898">com as pessoas da Daptone,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:42.898" end="00:06:44.058">sabe,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.058" end="00:06:44.881">que equipa maravilhosa que eles s&#227;o.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.881" end="00:06:46.190">E j&#225; viu es.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.190" end="00:06:48.866">o que aconteceu com a Sharon Jones, que, - Sim, sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:48.866" end="00:06:50.928">que, sabe, como voc&#234;,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:50.928" end="00:06:52.469">foi da completa obscuridade at&#233;,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52.484" end="00:06:55.048">quem sabe as alturas a que voc&#234;s poder&#227;o subir.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.048" end="00:06:56.455">Ent&#227;o, este,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56.455" end="00:06:58.647">deve ser um momento excitante para si?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:58.647" end="00:07:01.398">- Penso que Deus respondeu &#224;s minhas preces,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.398" end="00:07:03.440">sabe,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.440" end="00:07:05.606">perguntei-me a mim pr&#243;prio porque demorou tanto,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:05.606" end="00:07:07.023">mas n&#227;o podemos questionar Deus</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07.023" end="00:07:08.981">quando ele quer fazer coisas.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:08.981" end="00:07:11.915">Ent&#227;o, j&#225; eu com a minha idade avan&#231;ada, come&#231;ou a vir.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:11.915" end="00:07:13.482">- O que se segue?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.482" end="00:07:14.939">Quero dizer, est&#225; a pensar em grande?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:14.939" end="00:07:16.706">- Penso que o limite &#233; o c&#233;u.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:16.706" end="00:07:18.981">- Parab&#233;ns por este fant&#225;stico &#225;lbum.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:18.981" end="00:07:20.296">Independentemente do que aconte&#231;a com ele,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20.296" end="00:07:22.189">&#233; um trabalho fant&#225;stico.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22.189" end="00:07:24.498">Charleys Bradley na WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:24.667" end="00:07:27.897"/>
      <p begin="00:07:27.897" end="00:07:33.231">&#9834; Este mundo est&#225; a arder. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.231" end="00:07:38.647">&#9834; E ningu&#233;m quer assumir a culpa. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:38.647" end="00:07:43.821">&#9834; N&#227;o me digam como viver a minha vida. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:43.821" end="00:07:49.276">&#9834; Quando nunca sentiram a dor. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.276" end="00:07:55.314">&#9834; Ohhh. Ahhh. Ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.314" end="00:07:57.856">&#9834;Ohhh.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:57.856" end="00:08:00.569">&#9834; N&#227;o me v&#234;em chorar? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:00.569" end="00:08:02.400" region="top">&#9834; Ohhh... &#9834; </p>
      <p begin="00:08:02.400" end="00:08:04.315"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04.315" end="00:08:05.564" region="top">- N&#227;o sei quantos artistas </p>
      <p begin="00:08:05.564" end="00:08:07.230" region="top">chegaram aos 62 anos de idade </p>
      <p begin="00:08:07.230" end="00:08:08.955" region="top">e lan&#231;aram o seu &#225;lbum de estreia. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:09.722" end="00:08:11.458" region="top">Ele poder&#225; ser o primeiro. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.284" end="00:08:14.441" region="top">- Este tipo, ele est&#225; a p&#244;r </p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.441" end="00:08:16.440" region="top">a p&#244;r as coisas em andamento. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:16.440" end="00:08:18.715" region="top">Ele trabalhou muito arduamente, durante muito tempo. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:18.838" end="00:08:20.357" region="top">E espero que </p>
      <p begin="00:08:20.357" end="00:08:21.232" region="top">pessoas suficientes o ou&#231;am a cantar, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:21.232" end="00:08:22.647">para que-</p>
      <p begin="00:08:22.647" end="00:08:23.856">que ele possa ter a vida</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.856" end="00:08:25.632">que quer e tomar conta da sua fam&#237;lia.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:25.632" end="00:08:27.118"/>
      <p begin="00:08:27.118" end="00:08:30.190">&#9834; Uh. Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.190" end="00:08:32.606">&#9834; Estou a falar contigo rapariga. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:32.606" end="00:08:34.023">&#9834; Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34.023" end="00:08:36.125">&#9834; Apenas tu ... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36.125" end="00:08:37.814">Fui at&#233; ao Gabe</p>
      <p begin="00:08:37.814" end="00:08:39.981">porque achei que ele sabia o que estava a fazer.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:39.981" end="00:08:41.606">Senti que ele me podia dar uma ajuda,</p>
