      <p begin="01:10:48.141" end="01:10:50.704">-Ele est&#225; realmente a apanhar os detalhes todos.</p>
      <p begin="01:10:50.826" end="01:10:59.981"/>
      <p begin="01:10:59.981" end="01:11:02.794">Ahh!</p>
      <p begin="01:11:02.794" end="01:11:04.567">&#201; assim que sou.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:17.167" end="01:11:19.988">Woo.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:20.440" end="01:11:53.746"/>
      <p begin="01:11:53.746" end="01:11:55.763">-Porque quando eu deixar este mundo, este mundo n&#227;o me deve nada.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:55.902" end="01:11:57.423">-Devolve-me o meu d&#243;lar agora.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:00.067" end="01:12:01.636">-Sai de cima de mim.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:01.762" end="01:12:03.463">-Man, devolve-me o meu d&#243;lar.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:04.481" end="01:12:13.267"/>
      <p begin="01:12:13.267" end="01:12:14.327">-Oh, o meu passaporte, aguarde um minuto.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:14.465" end="01:12:35.156"/>
      <p begin="01:12:35.295" end="01:12:37.234">-Poupa a tua lagosta.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:38.863" end="01:12:41.744">-Jimmy, tu n&#227;o comes lagosta, d&#225;s-me sempre a mim.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:41.913" end="01:12:43.208">-Hoje vou come&#231;ar a com&#234;-la</p>
      <p begin="01:12:43.423" end="01:13:05.159"/>
      <p begin="01:13:05.406" end="01:13:09.310">-Disseste bem r&#225;pido que a moeda era tua. Eu vi-a.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:09.417" end="01:13:10.476">-Apanhei-a.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:10.629" end="01:14:03.410"/>
    </div>
